data.description: Introducing a stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath single-story home nestled in the charming community of Artesia Village in La Porte, Texas. This residence boasts spacious 9-foot ceilings, enhancing the feeling of openness and airiness throughout. Luxury vinyl plank flooring graces the common areas, providing both durability and a touch of elegance. The heart of the home, the kitchen, showcases sleek quartz countertops, 42-inch cabinetry with crown molding, and a convenient walk-in pantry. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas, creating a welcoming space for family and friends to gather. In the private quarters, you'll discover a master bedroom that defines comfort and luxury. The master bathroom features a separate shower and tub for your relaxation, while two separate closets offer ample storage space. Don't miss the opportunity to make this La Porte gem your own!
